Character class: data class container to hold all characters
Keyboard class: all methods and properties for the model keyboard
Exercise class: holds all info about an Exercise
ExcerciseStatus enum: enum to hold exercises status.
ExerciseDisplayArea class: this is the class where we need to control keyboard events
MainApp class: this the class that has the main layout for the app and contains all controls